===民族分佈===
富拉尼人主要居住在[[薩赫勒|薩赫勒]]地區，尤其是[[西非|西非]]地區。目前富拉尼人主要居住在[[茅利塔尼亞|茅利塔尼亞]]、[[迦納|迦納]]、[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]、幾內亞、[[甘比亞|甘比亞]]、[[馬利|馬利]]、[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]、[[獅子山共和國|獅子山]]、[[貝南|貝南]]、布基納法索、[[幾內亞比索|幾內亞比索]]、喀麥隆、[[象牙海岸|象牙海岸]]、[[尼日|尼日]]、[[查德|查德]]、[[多哥|多哥]]、[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]、中非共和國、[[賴比瑞亞|賴比瑞亞]]以及[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]和[[埃及|埃及]]的紅海岸。<ref name="Kays2011">{{cite book|first=Stanley J. |last=Kays |title=Cultivated Vegetables of the World: A Multilingual Onomasticon |publisher=Springer Science & Business Media |year=2011 |page=747 |isbn=9086867200}}</ref><ref name="gv">{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/gv.html |title=The World Factbook |publisher=Cia.gov |accessdate=2017-04-23 |archive-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919074825/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook//geos/gv.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ml">{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ml.html |title=The World Factbook |publisher=Cia.gov |accessdate=2017-04-23 |archive-date=2015-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110042640/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ml.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="uv">{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/uv.html |title=The World Factbook |publisher=Cia.gov |accessdate=2017-04-23 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224211237/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/uv.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cm">{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/cm.html |title=The World Factbook |publisher=Cia.gov |accessdate=2017-04-23 |archive-date=2016-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030061543/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/cm.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ng">{{cite web |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/ng.html |titl